net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.event

Class EventListenerList

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.event.EventListenerList

  • public class EventListenerList
extends Object
    The EventListenerList helps maintain event listeners. The references to the listeners can be added as a strong references or weak references. This class is thread safe.
    Author:
    Pat B. Double (double@i2rd.com)
